link: Amiram Eldar, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
mathematica: s = {}; m = 12; Do[n = 5^k; While[n <= 5^m, AppendTo[s, n]; n *= 3], {k, 0, m}]; FactorInteger[#][[-1, 1]] & /@ Union[s]  (* _Amiram Eldar_, Feb 07 2020 *)
